	<p class="ArticleContent" align="center"><font style="color:#000080;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">Design He Instructed in Person Nine Times</font></p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">&nbsp;</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">The general gymnasium of Mangyongdae Revolutionary School is permeated with the respected General Secretary <nobr>Kim Jong Un</nobr>&rsquo;s love for posterity.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Visiting the school in January several years ago, the respected General Secretary personally touched the chilly floor of the old gymnasium which was not properly heated and decided to provide the school with the best gymnasium in the world.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Later, he assigned the relevant designing unit to design the gymnasium and made sure that all necessary data for world were supplied to that end.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">He looked at the mock-up of the gymnasium presented by the designers and pointed out its defects.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">In this way, the design of the gymnasium was completed when he gave guidance to it for the ninth time and a gymnasium was built in a peculiar style at Mangyongdae Revolutionary School.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">The design he gave guidance to nine times－this shows the great love of the respected General Secretary who is anxious to pick even a star from the sky if it is for the good of the children.</p><p class="ArticleContent" align="right">Rodong Sinmun</p>	</td>
